HEADWORD: Biweekly
<hw>Bi"week`ly</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>bi-</ets> + <ets>weekly</ets>.]</ety> <def>Occurring or appearing
once every two weeks; fortnightly.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A
publication issued every two weeks.</def></def2> --
<wordforms><wf>Bi"week"ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

